    <h1>Easyily Build Super-Fast Static Websites!</h1>

    <h2>A ruby gem for creating simple static websites in minutes.</h2>
    
    <pre class="prettyprint" style="margin-top: 25px;"><code class="language-bsh">
  $ gem install scms
  $ scms --create mynewsite
  $ cd mynewsite
  $ scms --serve
    </code></pre>
    
    <p>scms also comes with a WYSIWYG editor called <a href="http://ipassexam.github.io/Air-Monkey/">Air-Monkey</a>, so your clients can edit their sites in point and click environment.</p>
